1.title: Fangoria, Halloween & Whatever Happened to the Clown from Poltergeist with Sean Clark
1.plot: Filmmaker Sean Clark (Horror's Hallowed Grounds) discusses his lifelong fascination with the horror genre, including his childhood introduction to Fangoria magazine and his screen-used clown prop from the classic 1982 film Poltergeist.

2.title: Collecting Vintage Star Wars Toys with Mike Mendez
2.plot: Filmmaker Mike Mendez (Tales of Halloween, Big Ass Spider) discusses his initial entrance into the world of collecting the Star Wars Early Bird Certificate Package as a boy.

3.title: Where Is It Now? The Saw from The Texas Chainsaw Massacre 2!
3.plot: Sean Clark shows off one of his many one-of-a-kind, screen-used props: the chainsaw from Tobe Hooper's 1986 cult classic horror-comedy, The Texas Chainsaw Massacre 2.

1.title: The Hills Run Red & Ones Customs 1/6 Scale Figures with Robert Meyer Burnett
1.plot: Filmmaker Robert Meyer Burnett (Free Enterprise) discusses his love of sixth scale representations of characters in film, including the Ones Customs Collectibles figure version of Babyface: the killer who appears in Burnett's own-produced 2009 film The Hills Run Red.

2.title: Tales of Halloween & Ones Customs 1/6 Scale Horror Figures with Mike Mendez
2.plot: Filmmaker Mike Mendez (Tales of Halloween, Big Ass Spider) discusses his collection of horror figures, model kits based on his own films, Ones Customs Collectibles figures and how his childhood toys inspired his career.

3.title: Ichi the Killer 1/6 Scale Figures & 80's Nostalgia with Robert Meyer Burnett
3.plot: Filmmaker Robert Meyer Burnett (The Hills Run Red, Free Enterprise) discusses the interrelated influences of 1980's pop culture on literature, music, film and collectibles, as well as his rare collection of exclusive mail-order-only Ichi the Killer figures.

4.title: Kenner's Alien Action Figure with Mike Mendez
4.plot: Filmmaker Mike Mendez (Tales of Halloween, Don't Kill It) discusses his collection of Alien collectibles, including a rare 1978 xenomorph figure release from Jenner, as well as an even rarer collectible: a Tupak Shakur action figure.

5.title: Star Crash with Robert Meyer Burnett's 1/6 Scale Caroline Munro Phicen Figure
5.plot: Filmmaker Robert Meyer Burnett "The Hills Run Red, Free Enterprise" discusses his love of collecting and Star Crash starlet Caroline Munro. From star child to spy, Caroline Munro has inspired cinema and young boys alike.

6.title: Indiana Jones & The Return of Mego Action Figures with Mike Mendez
6.plot: Filmmaker Mike Mendez (Tales of Halloween, The Convent) discusses his Indiana Jones collection, acquiring Comic Con limited releases, and his love of Mego's Mad Monster Series of the 1970's.

7.title: Axanar, Enterprise Model Kits & Mego's Romulan Action Figure with Robert Meyer Burnett
7.plot: Filmmaker Robert Meyer Burnett (Free Enterprise) discusses his love of collecting Star Trek memorabilia and filmmaking.

8.title: Go Back to the Future with Hot Toys' 1/6 Scale Delorean with Mike Mendez
8.plot: Filmmaker Mike Mendez (Tales of Halloween, Big Ass Spider) discusses his collection of Back to the Future collectibles from high end toy company Hot Toys, as well as his interest in screen-used props.

imdb.title: Collection Complete
plot: _Collection Complete_ (qv) is an in-depth look into the lives of filmmakers and artists and the collections that fuel their work.::Sean Decker
